{"id":3000,"date":"2025-06-05T13:38:15","date_gmt":"2025-06-05T06:38:15","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=3000"},"modified":"2025-06-09T10:19:37","modified_gmt":"2025-06-09T03:19:37","slug":"da-xin-mau-la-gi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/thong-tin-nganh\/da-xin-mau-la-gi\/","title":{"rendered":"Da x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u l\u00e0 g\u00ec? Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><b><i>Da x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/i><\/b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da b\u1ecb x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u thi\u1ebfu s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng khi\u1ebfn g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u00f4ng m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi, k\u00e9m r\u1ea1ng r\u1ee1. L\u00e0n da l\u00fac n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u, th\u00f4 r\u00e1p, xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1m n\u00e2u, t\u00e0n nhang ho\u1eb7c n\u1ebfp nh\u0103n li ti. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 m\u00e0 c\u00f2n khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 tin khi giao ti\u1ebfp. V\u1eady da s\u1ea1m x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u b\u1eaft ngu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb \u0111\u00e2u? L\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4i ph\u1ee5c l\u1ea1i l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh, s\u00e1ng m\u1ecbn? C\u00f9ng t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u ngay!<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"da-bi-xin-mau-la-gi\"><\/span><b>Da b\u1ecb x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u l\u00e0 g\u00ec?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><b>Da x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u l\u00e0 g\u00ec<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">? \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0n da m\u1ea5t \u0111i v\u1ebb r\u1ea1ng r\u1ee1 v\u1ed1n c\u00f3, tr\u1edf n\u00ean t\u1ed1i m\u00e0u, nh\u1ee3t nh\u1ea1t v\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng. Da c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n th\u00eam c\u00e1c d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u nh\u01b0 l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng to, n\u1ebfp nh\u0103n, \u0111\u1ed1m n\u00e2u ho\u1eb7c s\u1ea1m n\u00e1m. Khi <\/span><b>da b\u1ecb x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> v\u00e0 k\u00e9m t\u01b0\u01a1i t\u1eafn, t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t d\u1ec5 b\u1ecb gi\u00e0 nua, m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi, khi\u1ebfn b\u1ea1n m\u1ea5t \u0111i s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u1ed1n c\u00f3.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"nguyen-nhan-khien-da-bi-xin-mau-thieu-suc-song\"><\/span><b>Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn da b\u1ecb x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u thi\u1ebfu s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 khi\u1ebfn da s\u1ea1m x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u v\u00e0 m\u1ea5t \u0111i \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea1ng ng\u1eddi t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn nh\u1ea5t:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3760\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3760\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3760\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/24-1.webp\" alt=\"Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn da b\u1ecb x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u\" width=\"800\" height=\"581\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/24-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/24-1-300x218.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/24-1-768x558.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/24-1-600x436.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3760\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn da b\u1ecb x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"khong-bao-ve-da-truoc-anh-nang-mat-troi\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u00e1nh n\u1eafng m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tia UVA v\u00e0 UVB trong \u00e1nh n\u1eafng m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi l\u00e0 t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh k\u00edch th\u00edch s\u1ea3n sinh melanin \u2013 h\u1eafc s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00e1c h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a tia c\u1ef1c t\u00edm. Tuy nhi\u00ean, melanin c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u201cth\u1ee7 ph\u1ea1m\u201d khi\u1ebfn da b\u1ecb x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u v\u00e0 th\u00e2m s\u1ea1m. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng che ch\u1eafn k\u1ef9 c\u00e0ng, l\u00e0n da s\u1ebd nhanh ch\u00f3ng m\u1ea5t \u0111i \u0111\u1ed9 s\u00e1ng m\u1ecbn v\u00e0 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u l\u00e3o h\u00f3a nh\u01b0 n\u00e1m, t\u00e0n nhang.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"da-mat-nuoc\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da m\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m s\u1ebd tr\u1edf n\u00ean kh\u00f4 r\u00e1p, bong tr\u00f3c v\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng. Khi h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da suy y\u1ebfu, c\u00e1c t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i nh\u01b0 b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n, \u00f4 nhi\u1ec5m s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng x\u00e2m nh\u1eadp, khi\u1ebfn da b\u1ecb x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u thi\u1ebfu s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 m\u1ea5t \u0111i v\u1ebb c\u0103ng m\u1ecbn t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"anh-huong-tu-moi-truong-o-nhiem\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u1ea2nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1eeb m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u00f4 nhi\u1ec5m<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u00f4 nhi\u1ec5m ch\u1ee9a nhi\u1ec1u vi khu\u1ea9n v\u00e0 b\u1ee5i m\u1ecbn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da, l\u00e0m s\u1ea3n sinh c\u00e1c g\u1ed1c t\u1ef1 do, c\u1ea3n tr\u1edf qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t collagen. Theo th\u1eddi gian, l\u00e0n da s\u1ebd tr\u1edf n\u00ean th\u00f4 r\u00e1p, t\u1ed1i m\u00e0u v\u00e0 d\u1ea7n x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"te-bao-chet-tich-tu\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">T\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft t\u00edch t\u1ee5<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea9y t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, l\u1edbp da ch\u1ebft t\u00edch t\u1ee5 s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn l\u00e0n da kh\u00f4 r\u00e1p, s\u1ea1m \u0111en v\u00e0 b\u00edt t\u1eafc l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0m da b\u1ecb x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u m\u00e0 c\u00f2n c\u1ea3n tr\u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t t\u1eeb c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m skincare.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"lao-hoa-da\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e3o h\u00f3a da<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh l\u00e3o h\u00f3a t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, c\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi th\u00f3i quen sinh ho\u1ea1t kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 th\u1ee9c khuya, c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng k\u00e9o d\u00e0i, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m suy gi\u1ea3m collagen v\u00e0 elastin. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 da s\u1ea1m x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u, n\u1ebfp nh\u0103n xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u00f4ng gi\u00e0 nua h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3720\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3720\" style=\"width: 1200px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3720 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/38-LIEU-TRINH-PHUC-HOI-DA-MONG-YEU-LO-MAO-MACH_-1.webp\" alt=\"L\u00e3o ho\u00e1 da\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/38-LIEU-TRINH-PHUC-HOI-DA-MONG-YEU-LO-MAO-MACH_-1.webp 1200w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/38-LIEU-TRINH-PHUC-HOI-DA-MONG-YEU-LO-MAO-MACH_-1-300x200.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/38-LIEU-TRINH-PHUC-HOI-DA-MONG-YEU-LO-MAO-MACH_-1-1024x683.webp 1024w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/38-LIEU-TRINH-PHUC-HOI-DA-MONG-YEU-LO-MAO-MACH_-1-768x512.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/38-LIEU-TRINH-PHUC-HOI-DA-MONG-YEU-LO-MAO-MACH_-1-600x400.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3720\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>L\u00e3o ho\u00e1 da<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"thoi-quen-an-uong-sinh-hoat-thieu-khoa-hoc\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u00f3i quen \u0103n u\u1ed1ng, sinh ho\u1ea1t thi\u1ebfu khoa h\u1ecdc<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u1ee9c khuya, thi\u1ebfu ng\u1ee7, \u0103n u\u1ed1ng kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0nh m\u1ea1nh khi\u1ebfn c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1eddi gian ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i, t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o t\u1ebf b\u00e0o. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn da x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u thi\u1ebfu s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng do kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ee7 dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"lam-dung-my-pham\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u1ea1m d\u1ee5ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m qu\u00e1 m\u1ee9c, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m trang \u0111i\u1ec3m d\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb7c, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m b\u00edt t\u1eafc l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng, k\u00edch th\u00edch melanin s\u1ea3n sinh qu\u00e1 m\u1ee9c, d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn da b\u1ecb x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u v\u00e0 th\u00e2m s\u1ea1m.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"bi-quyet-cai-thien-da-xin-mau-thieu-suc-song-rang-ro-hon\"><\/span><b>B\u00ed quy\u1ebft c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n da x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u thi\u1ebfu s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng r\u1ea1ng r\u1ee1 h\u01a1n<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Da x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u l\u00e0 g\u00ec? \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng l\u00e0n da kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u, k\u00e9m t\u01b0\u01a1i t\u1eafn, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u00e8m theo d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng to, n\u1ebfp nh\u0103n, v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1m s\u1ea1m n\u00e1m. \u0110\u1ec3 kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c da b\u1ecb x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u v\u00e0 nhanh ch\u00f3ng l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i l\u00e0n da tr\u1eafng s\u00e1ng, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng 4 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3762\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3762\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3762\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/24-3-2.webp\" alt=\"B\u00ed quy\u1ebft c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n da x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/24-3-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/24-3-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/24-3-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/24-3-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3762\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>B\u00ed quy\u1ebft c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n da x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"loai-bo-te-bao-chet-dinh-ky\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ef3<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n da s\u1ea1m x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u, b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m l\u00e0 t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n. Vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y gi\u00fap lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf l\u1edbp t\u1ebf b\u00e0o ch\u1ebft t\u00edch t\u1ee5 tr\u00ean b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t, m\u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cho c\u00e1c d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t l\u00e0m tr\u1eafng da th\u1ea9m th\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. H\u00e3y l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m t\u1ea9y da ch\u1ebft nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, ch\u1ee9a AHA ho\u1eb7c BHA t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o lo\u1ea1i da c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n, \u0111\u1ec3 v\u1eeba l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u v\u1eeba tr\u00e1nh g\u00e2y t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"bo-sung-vitamin-va-khoang-chat-can-thiet\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u1ed5 sung Vitamin v\u00e0 kho\u00e1ng ch\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh t\u1eeb b\u00ean trong l\u00e0 ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a gi\u00fap kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c da x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u thi\u1ebfu s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng. M\u1ed9t ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng, gi\u00e0u Vitamin v\u00e0 kho\u00e1ng ch\u1ea5t s\u1ebd h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o da, th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y tu\u1ea7n ho\u00e0n m\u00e1u v\u00e0 t\u0103ng s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00e1ng cho l\u00e0n da. H\u00e3y ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3756\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3756\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3756\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-5.webp\" alt=\"Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p \u0103n u\u1ed1ng khoa h\u1ecdc\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-5.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-5-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-5-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/25-5-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3756\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p \u0103n u\u1ed1ng khoa h\u1ecdc<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vitamin C, E, B: Gi\u00fap da \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u, s\u00e1ng kh\u1ecfe.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">K\u1ebdm, axit b\u00e9o: Duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u01b0\u1edbc, rau xanh, tr\u00e1i c\u00e2y t\u01b0\u01a1i: Thanh l\u1ecdc c\u01a1 th\u1ec3, ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba \u0111\u1ed9c t\u1ed1 t\u00edch t\u1ee5.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, \u0111\u1eebng qu\u00ean t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 d\u1ee5c th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 k\u00edch th\u00edch l\u01b0u th\u00f4ng m\u00e1u, mang \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e0n da h\u1ed3ng h\u00e0o v\u00e0 r\u1ea1ng r\u1ee1.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"bao-ve-da-truoc-tac-dong-cua-moi-truong\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Khi ra ngo\u00e0i, h\u00e3y \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o l\u00e0n da c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch che ch\u1eafn v\u1edbi m\u0169, \u00e1o kho\u00e1c, k\u00ednh r\u00e2m,&#8230; \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a \u00e1nh n\u1eafng m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi v\u00e0 \u00f4 nhi\u1ec5m l\u00ean da. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, thoa kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y, d\u00f9 \u1edf trong nh\u00e0 hay ngo\u00e0i tr\u1eddi, l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu. Ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 <\/span><b>SPF t\u1eeb 30 tr\u1edf l\u00ean<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> v\u00e0 ph\u1ed5 r\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3761\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3761\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-3761\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/24-2-2.webp\" alt=\"B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/24-2-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/24-2-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/24-2-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/05\/24-2-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3761\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><em>B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"su-dung-san-pham-duong-trang-chuyen-sau\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u01b0\u1ee1ng tr\u1eafng chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n da x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u l\u00e0 g\u00ec v\u00e0 l\u00e0m s\u00e1ng da nhanh ch\u00f3ng, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m d\u01b0\u1ee1ng da chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u. Khi ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m, h\u00e3y \u01b0u ti\u00ean c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vitamin C, E, Bisabolol: Th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t collagen, l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Than ho\u1ea1t t\u00ednh: Lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf \u0111\u1ed9c t\u1ed1 v\u00e0 b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n t\u1eeb m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Niacinamide, peptides, Peptides, Zinc Glycinate: \u1ee8c ch\u1ebf s\u1ea3n sinh melanin, gi\u1ea3m th\u00e2m n\u00e1m.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Retinol: H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o da, gi\u1ea3m n\u1ebfp nh\u0103n v\u00e0 s\u1ea1m n\u00e1m.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">V\u1edbi b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft c\u1ee7a GSC tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y, b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eafm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1ch c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n da x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u thi\u1ebfu s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 nhanh ch\u00f3ng l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i l\u00e0n da r\u1ea1ng r\u1ee1. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang b\u0103n kho\u0103n v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng skincare da b\u1ecb x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u hay mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm serum d\u00e0nh cho da kh\u00f4 x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u, \u0111\u1eebng ng\u1ea7n ng\u1ea1i kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p l\u00e0m \u0111\u1eb9p khoa h\u1ecdc \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u. Hy v\u1ecdng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 da x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u l\u00e0 g\u00ec v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m tr\u1eafng da x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u!<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>\u1eady da s\u1ea1m x\u1ec9n m\u00e0u b\u1eaft ngu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb \u0111\u00e2u? L\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4i ph\u1ee5c l\u1ea1i l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh, s\u00e1ng m\u1ecbn? C\u00f9ng t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u ngay!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":3759,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[16],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-3000","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-thong-tin-nganh"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3000","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/7"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3000"}],"version-history":[{"count":5,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3000\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":3979,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3000\/revisions\/3979"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3759"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=3000"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=3000"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=3000"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}